{"word":"G1727 - ἐναντίος - enantíos - en-an-tee'-os - Against","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐναντίος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enantíos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-an-tee'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Against</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினோதமான, எதிரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"over against; opposite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1725 - ἔναντι - énanti - en'-an-tee/1725\">G1725</a>; <i>opposite</i>; figuratively <i>antagonistic:</i> - (over) against, contrary.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}